pageProduct.name: Thompson's CoQ10 300mg 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's High Strength Ultra CoQ10 300 High strength, powerful antioxidant that supports cardiovascular health and energy production.

Thompson's High Strength Ultra CoQ10 300 supports cardiovascular health and helps maintain the healthy function of the heart muscle. It may also help reduce the frequency of migraines. CoQ10 supports energy production and may assist in the temporary relief of fatigue. It is a potent antioxidant that helps protect cells from free radical damage and assists in the maintenance of general wellbeing.

Size: 60caps

KEY FEATURES

• Supports cardiovascular health.
• Helps maintain the healthy function of the heart muscle.
• May help reduce the frequency of migraines.
• Supports energy production and may assist in the temporary relief of fatigue.
• Potent antioxidant that helps protect cells from free radical damage.
• Assists in the maintenance of general wellbeing.

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. Do not take while on warfarin therapy without medical advice.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each capsule contains:
Ubidecarenone (Co-Enzyme Q10): 300mg

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
